    "We continue this process until a full loop through all parameters does not yield any improvement.",
    "By improvement in performance we mean that all the following are satisfied:",
    "• The in-sample Sharpe ratio increases.",
    "• The in-sample annualized turnover is no more than 50.",
    "• The in-sample maximum leverage is no more than 2."
